request.description:
Remove items from a specific catalog list.

Valid listTypes:
- gender, pronouns, likes, interests, hereFor, languages

Examples:
- Remove language: {"listType": "languages", "items": ["Russian"]}
- Remove hereFor: {"listType": "hereFor", "items": ["fun"]}
- Remove interests: {"listType": "interests", "items": ["pets"]}
